Title: An Act Changing the Name of Butuan Primary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Sofronio Castro Primary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 760
An Act Changing the Name of Butuan Primary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Sofronio Castro Primary School
Section 1. The name of Butuan Primary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao del Sur, is changed to Sofronio Castro Primary School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
